#Merciful Witch Doctor		KEY:Shaman Archetype ~ Merciful Witch Doctor		CATEGORY:Archetype			TYPE:Archetype.ShamanArchetype.ShamanHex4.ShamanHex12.ShamanHex8.ShamanHex10										!PREALIGN:LE,NE,CE	PRECLASS:1,Shaman=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Shaman Archetype ~ Merciful Witch Doctor],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE.ShamanHex4,TYPE.ShamanHex12,TYPE.ShamanHex8,TYPE.ShamanHex10]																											DESC:The merciful witch doctor is a healer who specializes in afflictions of the body and soul. Often misunderstood, she protects her tribe with healing powers, powerful defensive magic, and her own divine "witchcraft."																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			ABILITY:Shaman Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Merciful Witch Doctor ~ Alignment|PRECLASS:1,Shaman=1	ABILITY:Shaman Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Merciful Witch Doctor ~ Merciful Channeling|PRECLASS:1,Shaman=3	ABILITY:Shaman Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Merciful Witch Doctor ~ Merciful Healing|PRECLASS:1,Shaman=3		ABILITY:Shaman Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Merciful Witch Doctor ~ Channel Mercies|PRECLASS:1,Shaman=3		ABILITY:Shaman Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Merciful Witch Doctor ~ Counter Curse|PRECLASS:1,Shaman=8	ABILITY:Shaman Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Merciful Witch Doctor ~ Countering Hex|PRECLASS:1,Shaman=10							COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.113	ASPECT:Archetype Base Class|Shaman


